        <h1>Manual</h1>
        <p>Welcome to the HighRoller Hub support manual. Here you will find guidance on how to use the website and troubleshoot common issues.</p>

        <h2>Getting Started</h2>
        <p>1. <strong>Register or Log In:</strong> Click on the "Sign Up" or "Log In" button on the homepage. Fill in the required details to create an account or access your existing account.</p>
        <p>2. <strong>Explore Categories:</strong> Use the navigation bar to browse through categories like Cars, Yachts, Penthouses, and Planes. Each category contains listings with detailed information.</p>

        <h2>How to Add Items to Wishlist or Cart</h2>
        <p>1. <strong>Find an Item:</strong> Navigate to the item you are interested in by browsing the categories or using the search bar.</p>
        <p>2. <strong>Add to Wishlist:</strong> Click on the "Add to Wishlist" button to save the item for later.</p>
        <p>3. <strong>Add to Cart:</strong> If you are ready to purchase, click on the "Add to Cart" button. You can view your cart at any time by clicking the cart icon in the navigation bar.</p>

        <h2>How to Purchase Items</h2>
        <p>1. <strong>Review Your Cart:</strong> Go to your cart and review the items you have added. Ensure the details and quantities are correct.</p>
        <p>2. <strong>Proceed to Checkout:</strong> Click on the "Purchase" button. You will be prompted to confirm your payment method and complete the transaction.</p>
        <p>3. <strong>Transaction Confirmation:</strong> Once the payment is successful, you will receive a confirmation email with the transaction details.</p>

        <h2>How to Sell Items</h2>
        <p>1. <strong>Go to the Sell Section:</strong> Navigate to the "Sell" section from the navigation bar and select the category of the item you want to sell (e.g., Cars, Yachts).</p>
        <p>2. <strong>Fill in the Details:</strong> Provide all the required details about the item, including images, price, and description.</p>
        <p>3. <strong>Submit the Listing:</strong> Click on the "Submit" button to list your item for sale. Your listing will be visible to potential buyers.</p>

        <h2>How to Manage Your Profile</h2>
        <p>1. <strong>Access Your Profile:</strong> Click on your username in the navigation bar to access your profile page.</p>
        <p>2. <strong>Edit Profile:</strong> Update your personal details, profile picture, and contact information as needed.</p>
        <p>3. <strong>View Purchase History:</strong> Check your purchase history to see all completed transactions.</p>

        <h2>Troubleshooting</h2>
        <p>If you encounter any issues, please contact support via:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Email: support@highrollerhub.com</li>
            <li>Phone: 1-800-700-900</li>
            <li>Live Chat: Available 24/7</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>FAQs</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Q:</strong> How do I reset my password?<br>
                <strong>A:</strong> Click on the "Forgot Password" link on the login page and follow the instructions to reset your password.
            </li>
            <li><strong>Q:</strong> Can I sell multiple items at once?<br>
                <strong>A:</strong> Yes, you can list multiple items for sale by navigating to the respective "Sell" section for Cars, Yachts, Penthouses, or Planes.
            </li>
            <li><strong>Q:</strong> How do I check my purchase history?<br>
                <strong>A:</strong> Go to your profile page, and you will find a section displaying your purchase history.
            </li>
            <li><strong>Q:</strong> What payment methods are supported?<br>
                <strong>A:</strong> Currently, we support credit/debit cards and wallet balance for transactions.
            </li>
            <li><strong>Q:</strong> How do I contact the seller?<br>
                <strong>A:</strong> Seller contact details are available on the item details page.
            </li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Additional Support</h2>
        <p>If you need further assistance, here are some additional resources:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Live Chat:</strong> Use the chatbot below for instant help.</li>
            <li><strong>Community Forum:</strong> Join discussions and get help from other users.</li>
            <li><strong>Documentation:</strong> Visit our <a href="/docs">documentation page</a> for detailed guides.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Tips for a Better Experience</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Ensure your profile is complete with accurate contact details for smooth transactions.</li>
            <li>Use filters on the "Buy" pages to narrow down your search results.</li>
            <li>Regularly check your wishlist and cart to avoid missing out on deals.</li>
            <li>Keep your wallet balance topped up for quick purchases.</li>
        </ul>
